12:02.855 --> 12:05.022
Oh, shit, yes.
No, no, no. No, no.

12:05.024 --> 12:06.724
H-he was...He meant...
Yeah, what?

12:06.726 --> 12:08.792
N-not... Oh, yeah?
Yeah, say it, man.

12:08.794 --> 12:09.994
I'm not gonna say it
in that context.

12:09.996 --> 12:13.063
