[ Touchscreen clicking ]

13:09.956 --> 13:11.722
Yeah, okay, and the first
dictionary definition

13:11.724 --> 13:14.658
of that word is...
Oh, great, you're that guy?

13:14.660 --> 13:18.929
"A narrow opening or crack,
as in -- in someone's armor."

13:18.931 --> 13:21.065
