if you just give it to us.

20:32.831 --> 20:34.264
Yeah, do you have a warrant,
old man?

20:34.266 --> 20:39.169
Oh, what's that? You don't?
Oh, suck on my first amendment.

20:39.171 --> 20:40.137
Come on, Morris.

20:40.139 --> 20:42.472
Yeah, why don't you do
your homework next time?

20:42.474 --> 20:44.474
Wikipedia the constitution.

20:44.476 --> 20:46.243
I don't like him.

20:46.245 --> 20:48.078
Men: ♪ hey ♪

20:48.080 --> 20:50.847
Yeah, that's right.
I'm a maverick.

20:50.849 --> 20:54.084
Billy Evans?
[ Footsteps approach ]

20:54.086 --> 20:56.053
Um...

20:58.490 --> 20:59.556
Yeah?

20:59.558 --> 21:00.390
[ Snaps fingers ]

21:00.392 --> 21:03.593
Listen to me. I'm in some
really deep shit right now.

21:03.595 --> 21:06.229
