is for you to give me

21:06.231 --> 21:07.898
what Nate Parker gave you.

21:07.900 --> 21:09.132
Look, I'm gonna say
the same thing

21:09.134 --> 21:10.434
I said to those guys.
I'm a journalist.

21:10.436 --> 21:13.370
I'm not gonna let you
and your chain gang come --

21:13.372 --> 21:15.439
<i> lo tengo. Vámonos.</i>

21:15.441 --> 21:18.542
Hey. I'm sorry you got
mixed up in this.

21:18.544 --> 21:21.044
But you have to understand.

